{"type": "article", "id": 16622, "title": "盆景灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-27T06:00:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060600452035CYIUq2k0alZnwJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t如何让室内多一点绿色？来自加拿大多伦多的 Object Interface 做了这盏盆景吊灯。他们在白色的铝制圆形灯罩上放上了土壤和植物，在灯罩上用了一种特殊的粉末，以便让用电的灯可以承受盆栽的湿度。不开灯的时候，则是吊挂的盆栽，而当夜晚开灯时，绿色的植物就能在灯光下显得格外青翠。<a href=\"http://www.objectinterface.ca/shop/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143936JvKkR3eMiYUaC01z.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143936ptkuCcw6mhF2RPqD.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"525\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614393726SvGfkIDQCgBmKb.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.334\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143937iCrTxoYlVq9JUwn8.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"418\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143938E7dp6FNHeKZ3sjmS.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"608\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.608\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}